Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:05.19,Base,,0,0,0,,The dorm mother's box lunches\Nalways look so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.19,0:00:08.40,Base,,0,0,0,,You think so? Looks average to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.50,0:00:11.42,Base,,0,0,0,,It's pretty brown.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.42,0:00:14.76,Base,,0,0,0,,I wish it had some cuter stuff in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.89,0:00:18.97,Base,,0,0,0,,Food always tastes great\Nwhen it's made just for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.97,0:00:19.74,Base,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.74,0:00:20.35,Base,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.35,0:00:23.73,Base,,0,0,0,,Hey, Narata isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.73,0:00:26.27,Base,,0,0,0,,Huh? Ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.24,0:00:55.49,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}Everyone dreams of becoming a superstar at least once
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.49,0:01:00.77,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}So that you can make the world envious
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.77,0:01:03.52,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}1, 2, 3, quick like Allegro
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.52,0:01:05.79,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}Hold that hand and come
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.79,0:01:10.34,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}Let's build a rainbow together at Andante
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.53,0:01:16.60,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}You aren't anyone right now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.60,0:01:21.71,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}So any of your future can come true
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.71,0:01:27.72,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}Your dream is just beginning
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.21,0:01:32.39,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}Little by little, you can become yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.39,0:01:38.31,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}Tomorrow's gonna blow another wind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.31,0:01:42.23,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}So dream as many times as you want
