Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.62,0:02:08.96,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"The Teddy Bear"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.71,0:02:08.98,Base,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.18,0:02:13.95,Base,,0,0,0,,You know, if you eat alone out here,\Nthe second-years will get on your case.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.95,0:02:17.38,Base,,0,0,0,,I don't want to eat lunch\Nin that tiny locker room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.38,0:02:20.19,Base,,0,0,0,,And making small talk\Nwith everyone's such a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.19,0:02:23.38,Base,,0,0,0,,How are things going with\Nyour roommate, Watanabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.38,0:02:25.25,Base,,0,0,0,,She seems fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.38,0:02:28.00,Base,,0,0,0,,Not in the least! She's not "fun" at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:32.88,Base,,0,0,0,,She's so loud, she doesn't listen,\N and she can't read the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.36,0:02:36.59,Base,,0,0,0,,She's always rolling off the bed,\Nshe never gets up on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.59,0:02:38.40,Base,,0,0,0,,I wish I could change rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.40,0:02:39.57,Base,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.78,0:02:42.50,Base,,0,0,0,,You've changed a little, Ai.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.29,0:02:46.27,Base,,0,0,0,,You've never taken interest in other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.71,0:02:48.06,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm not interested in her!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.82,0:02:53.15,Base,,0,0,0,,She just keeps forcing\Nherself into my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.15,0:02:54.22,Base,,0,0,0,,She's so annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.22,0:02:58.95,Base,,0,0,0,,I don't know. It seems like\Nyou can't take your eyes off her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.07,0:03:05.62,Base,,0,0,0,,You don't get it, Taichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.54,0:03:09.50,Base,,0,0,0,,You don't get how\Nunbearably annoying she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:11.92,Base,,0,0,0,,I don't think she's a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:13.54,Base,,0,0,0,,You should be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:17.16,Base,,0,0,0,,I don't need friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.16,0:03:18.88,Base,,0,0,0,,If I want to talk, I'll talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.42,0:03:21.51,Base,,0,0,0,,I can never be friends with Watanabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.77,0:03:26.28,Base,,0,0,0,,Ai! Where were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.28,0:03:27.01,Base,,0,0,0,,Nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.30,0:03:30.32,Base,,0,0,0,,I thought you might be in the bathroom,\Nbut you were gone so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.32,0:03:32.35,Base,,0,0,0,,Are you feeling okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.35,0:03:33.85,Base,,0,0,0,,Did you eat lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.85,0:03:34.46,Base,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:39.06,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm worried about you not eating enough, Ai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.06,0:03:40.43,Base,,0,0,0,,You needn't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.25,0:03:44.29,Base,,0,0,0,,Don't say that! We're friends, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.46,0:03:48.67,Base,,0,0,0,,We're not friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.59,0:04:07.21,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Hana no Michi: Flower Way"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.89,0:04:06.72,Base,,0,0,0,,If I wait here, maybe I'll see Naracchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:11.88,Base,,0,0,0,,But we're roommates!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.88,0:04:14.69,Base,,0,0,0,,I want to be friends with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.75,0:04:19.16,Base,,0,0,0,,I don't really want to be\Nfriends with anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.26,0:04:20.01,Base,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.46,0:04:25.12,Base,,0,0,0,,Dealing with people is annoying\Nand a waste of my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.58,0:04:26.47,Base,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.77,0:04:29.50,Base,,0,0,0,,Hey, you girls! No shouting in the halls!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.88,0:04:30.99,Base,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:32.62,Base,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.60,0:04:36.88,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't need friends.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.92,0:04:41.72,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just want to be as far away\Nas possible from the world of men.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.36,0:04:43.86,Base,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100}{\i1}That's all I want.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.35,0:04:49.93,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The words "you're so pretty!"\Nand "what a cutie!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:52.98,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}have always meant "hello" to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:55.27,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Narata Family Memorial Event"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.48,0:04:59.03,Base,,0,0,0,,My goodness, Ai,\Nyou just keep getting cuter!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.03,0:05:01.70,Base,,0,0,0,,I can't tell which one of you is the doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.01,0:05:04.01,Base,,0,0,0,,What a big teddy bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.01,0:05:05.55,Base,,0,0,0,,My daddy bought it for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.55,0:05:07.54,Base,,0,0,0,,Wow, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.99,0:05:09.10,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's not true.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.10,0:05:13.13,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's just what my mom said,\Nso it's probably not true.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.48,0:05:16.81,Base,,0,0,0,,So, who is your daddy, Ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.81,0:05:17.69,Base,,0,0,0,,I dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.69,0:05:19.30,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's the truth.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.98,0:05:23.53,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My mom is the famous\Nmovie actress Narata Kimiko.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.53,0:05:25.99,Base,,0,0,0,,Ai's such a cutie.\NNo wonder she's popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:28.62,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My uncle Taichi is a ballet dancer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.62,0:05:29.56,Base,,0,0,0,,That's not why.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.24,0:05:33.83,Base,,0,0,0,,They just want to know who her father is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.83,0:05:35.77,Base,,0,0,0,,Well, so do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:42.41,Base,,0,0,0,,You know what the old man\Nin Hachioji said?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.41,0:05:47.20,Base,,0,0,0,,"You siblings keep chasing men's asses."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.93,0:05:52.76,Base,,0,0,0,,Hey, Narata!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.76,0:05:56.73,Base,,0,0,0,,Your mom was popping her titties on TV last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.73,0:05:59.85,Base,,0,0,0,,Your mom's titties are jiggly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.85,0:06:01.31,Base,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.31,0:06:03.57,Base,,0,0,0,,Boys are the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.57,0:06:05.90,Base,,0,0,0,,Be little considerate to Ai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.90,0:06:07.76,Base,,0,0,0,,It's okay, I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.24,0:06:15.91,Base,,0,0,0,,My mom's working really hard.\NI've never been ashamed of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.91,0:06:16.77,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's also a lie.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.87,0:06:20.83,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've never even seen any of my mom's movies.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.43,0:06:23.72,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But my mom always tells me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.55,0:06:27.26,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that I'm the reason she works so hard.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.26,0:06:29.61,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And that cute girls\Nhave to 'tough it out.'{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.11,0:06:34.82,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It happened around the time I'd\Ngotten way bigger than Papa Bear.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.27,0:06:38.23,Base,,0,0,0,,This is Mr. Seiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.02,0:06:43.21,Base,,0,0,0,,He might be your new daddy someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.28,0:06:47.23,Base,,0,0,0,,It's real nice to meet you, Ai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.23,0:06:48.47,Base,,0,0,0,,Hope we get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.66,0:06:56.45,Base,,0,0,0,,It's nice to meet you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.45,0:07:01.32,Base,,0,0,0,,Mr. Seiji is such a nice guy, and he's\Ngonna live with us from here on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.54,0:07:02.22,Base,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.83,0:07:06.59,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My mom never told me where she met him,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.59,0:07:10.43,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}or what he did for a living.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.34,0:07:13.40,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But that wasn't new.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.40,0:07:15.58,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She never told me anything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:26.00,Base,,0,0,0,,Almost got it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.23,0:07:28.07,Base,,0,0,0,,Yes!
