Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.04,0:07:40.12,Base,,0,0,0,,You're such a cutie, Ai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.12,0:07:46.21,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His smile made my stomach turn,\Nbut it must've just been my imagination.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.21,0:07:49.33,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I mean, my mom picked him out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.94,0:07:51.34,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He couldn't be bad.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.34,0:07:53.24,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He never even got mad at me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.14,0:07:57.72,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So when he happened to be outside\Nthe door when I got out of the bath,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.72,0:08:01.48,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}or when his footsteps stopped\N in front of my door,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.48,0:08:03.19,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it all had be a coincidence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.77,0:08:07.14,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My mom's smart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.15,0:08:09.33,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All grown-ups are.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.19,0:08:12.71,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They all know so much more than the children.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.71,0:08:14.66,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They'd never be wrong.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.78,0:08:17.75,Base,,0,0,0,,Ai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.54,0:08:26.08,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm off to my one-week location shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.08,0:08:27.86,Base,,0,0,0,,Be good for Mr. Seiji, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.25,0:08:30.21,Base,,0,0,0,,Do your best at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.76,0:08:34.47,Base,,0,0,0,,And, uh, come home soon, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.63,0:08:39.85,Base,,0,0,0,,What? C'mon, you're too old\Nfor this baby nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.85,0:08:42.38,Base,,0,0,0,,Listen to Mr. Seiji now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.48,0:08:44.48,Base,,0,0,0,,Okay, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.48,0:08:49.69,Base,,0,0,0,,You know I'm working myself\Nto death for you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.03,0:08:55.32,Base,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.32,0:08:57.32,Base,,0,0,0,,You're so good at this, Miki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.32,0:09:01.87,Base,,0,0,0,,Ai, it's getting dark!\NYou should head home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.87,0:09:02.50,Base,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.95,0:09:05.54,Base,,0,0,0,,Here, I made some cupcakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.54,0:09:07.19,Base,,0,0,0,,Take some home with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.38,0:09:11.82,Base,,0,0,0,,Wow! You made these?\NYou didn't buy them at a store?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.13,0:09:15.80,Base,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.39,0:09:22.26,Base,,0,0,0,,Ai doesn't go on playdates very often.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.26,0:09:23.12,Base,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.74,0:09:26.42,Base,,0,0,0,,She's such a beauty, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.42,0:09:27.59,Base,,0,0,0,,Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.82,0:09:41.66,Base,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.88,0:09:54.84,Base,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.63,0:09:58.98,Base,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.14,0:10:03.60,Base,,0,0,0,,You're home late.\NI was so worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.35,0:10:14.11,Base,,0,0,0,,I wasn't sure what you liked to eat,\Nso I ordered a whole bunch of things.
