Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.16,0:10:20.45,Base,,0,0,0,,No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.45,0:10:22.79,Base,,0,0,0,,I got a cupcake from my friend's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.75,0:10:30.54,Base,,0,0,0,,Really? That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.54,0:10:34.89,Base,,0,0,0,,Y'know, I really want to be\Nfriends with you, Ai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.98,0:10:37.71,Base,,0,0,0,,B-But we are friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.55,0:10:40.97,Base,,0,0,0,,Really? Then to prove it,
