Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.23,0:11:33.65,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He made me a dirty slut.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.65,0:11:37.53,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, no. What if I get pregnant?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.86,0:11:42.78,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe if I tie my tummy real tight,\Nit won't get big.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.70,0:11:48.33,Base,,0,0,0,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.33,0:11:50.63,Base,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?\NI'm in the middle of a shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.91,0:11:53.38,Base,,0,0,0,,Please come home quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.38,0:11:56.97,Base,,0,0,0,,God, you've been such a baby lately!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.09,0:11:58.80,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm scared of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.80,0:12:01.55,Base,,0,0,0,,Of who? Mr. Seiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.55,0:12:04.43,Base,,0,0,0,,He's always staring at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.93,0:12:11.10,Base,,0,0,0,,And he waits for me\Nin front of my room! And he--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.10,0:12:13.65,Base,,0,0,0,,Here's the thing, Ai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.65,0:12:17.59,Base,,0,0,0,,It's just girls being self-conscious is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.28,0:12:20.61,Base,,0,0,0,,I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.61,0:12:22.40,Base,,0,0,0,,But today he--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.40,0:12:27.49,Base,,0,0,0,,Come on, Ai. What am I going to do\Nwith a little girl like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.20,0:12:35.29,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I actually knew everything all along.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.29,0:12:40.13,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My mom wasn't working hard for me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.13,0:12:43.34,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She loved work more than she loved me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.34,0:12:47.18,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My daddy didn't buy me this bear.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.14,0:12:52.39,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because my mom's an actress,\Nand my dad's not around,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.39,0:12:56.44,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}if I'm not perfect, everyone will\Nstart gossiping about her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:13:00.86,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why I pretended to be\Na happy little girl.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.86,0:13:05.20,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fad(0, 400)}I lied to everyone and stuffed\Nall those feelings down inside.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.82,0:13:09.20,Base,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0, 200)}I won't be lonely! I'll be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.37,0:13:14.09,Base,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0, 200)}My daddy got it for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.83,0:13:18.59,Base,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0, 200)}Mommy! Hey, Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.29,0:13:20.67,Base,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0, 170)}I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.34,0:13:26.13,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fad(0, 350)}Now nobody can stuff\Nanything else inside me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.56,0:13:40.11,Base,,0,0,0,,Ai, are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.07,0:13:43.19,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm coming in, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.79,0:13:55.67,Base,,0,0,0,,What happened to your hair? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:09.54,Base,,0,0,0,,Do you want me to do anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.22,0:14:14.94,Base,,0,0,0,,Put a lock on my door, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.75,0:14:21.99,Base,,0,0,0,,A few days later, when my mom came back,\Nshe had a huge fight with Taichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.65,0:14:26.53,Base,,0,0,0,,Here's the key to your room, Ai.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.53,0:14:28.07,Base,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.07,0:14:29.82,Base,,0,0,0,,I have one more thing for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.20,0:14:32.48,Base,,0,0,0,,It's a lucky charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.74,0:14:36.23,Base,,0,0,0,,A key to my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.79,0:14:39.73,Base,,0,0,0,,If anything bad happens,\Nyou can run away to my place anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.67,0:14:48.80,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Years passed, and soon,\NI was in junior high.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.89,0:14:53.14,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That man was still\Nleeching off of my family.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.14,0:14:56.77,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The lock on my door\Nkept any danger at bay,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.77,0:14:59.42,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and I learned that you can't\Nget pregnant from kissing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.98,0:15:03.73,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even still, I never felt safe.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.73,0:15:08.40,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The other kids started to call me\Nan emotionless "noh mask"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.40,0:15:12.95,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and it wasn't long before\NI lost all my friends.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.66,0:15:18.50,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pigs. I wish all men would die.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.96,0:15:24.34,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}These thoughts rang out through my head as\NI imagined mowing down men with gunfire.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.88,0:15:27.88,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Taichi can live, I guess.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.05,0:15:33.45,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"JPX48 Producer Kuroge Shun"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.18,0:15:33.45,Base,,0,0,0,,JPX48?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.64,0:15:37.54,Base,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's an idol group I'm producing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.93,0:15:41.96,Base,,0,0,0,,It's a group of girls ages 14 and up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.23,0:15:43.71,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An all-girl group.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.73,0:15:49.65,Base,,0,0,0,,When I saw your daughter, Ms. Narata,\NI knew she'd be a perfect fit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.65,0:15:52.70,Base,,0,0,0,,She's no good.\NShe's just not the type.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.70,0:15:54.85,Base,,0,0,0,,You see, that's what makes her perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.85,0:15:56.91,Base,,0,0,0,,We need cool-headed girls like her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.91,0:15:59.70,Base,,0,0,0,,Our studio's just down in Akihabara.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.70,0:16:02.24,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Akiba. That's where Taichi lives!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.79,0:16:03.69,Base,,0,0,0,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.79,0:16:04.85,Base,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.09,0:16:06.15,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was so stupid.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.05,0:16:11.88,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't even stop to think about the\Ntarget audience of an all-girl idol group.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.88,0:16:13.68,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Years later...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:19.76,Base,,0,0,0,,Let go, creep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.18,0:16:24.11,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...it would lead to\Nmy cold words that day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.27,0:16:27.55,Base,,0,0,0,,Ugh, I can't believe her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.65,0:16:31.93,Base,,0,0,0,,That Watanabe Sarasa! She must've\Nsaid something to you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.53,0:16:34.91,Base,,0,0,0,,She must've ticked you off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:38.31,Base,,0,0,0,,It was my fault, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.41,0:16:41.81,Base,,0,0,0,,You're so sweet, Narata.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.71,0:16:49.34,Base,,0,0,0,,Just tell me if something unpleasant\N happens with Watanabe again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:51.46,Base,,0,0,0,,I'll handle it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.84,0:16:57.18,Base,,0,0,0,,In tap dancing, you produce a rhythm\Nwith the toe, ball, and heel of your foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.18,0:16:59.56,Base,,0,0,0,,You become a musical\Ninstrument as you dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.56,0:17:03.23,Base,,0,0,0,,Feel the rhythm in your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.23,0:17:07.84,Base,,0,0,0,,Ball, heel, ball, heel, heel, heel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.84,0:17:11.44,Base,,0,0,0,,Tap-tap, tap-tap, tap, tap.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.44,0:17:12.28,Base,,0,0,0,,Try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.66,0:17:18.49,Base,,0,0,0,,You catch on quick, Narata.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.97,0:17:22.12,Base,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't be surprised,\N given your stage experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.00,0:17:25.82,Base,,0,0,0,,Watanabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.55,0:17:27.92,Base,,0,0,0,,You're too loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.92,0:17:28.90,Base,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.13,0:17:33.26,Base,,0,0,0,,Your steps are too heavy!\NImagine they're being sucked down to the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.26,0:17:34.53,Base,,0,0,0,,Light movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.84,0:17:38.09,Base,,0,0,0,,Mr. Narata told me the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.09,0:17:40.72,Base,,0,0,0,,He says I've got good control,\Nbut I'm heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.72,0:17:43.25,Base,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! Yamada!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.23,0:17:46.67,Base,,0,0,0,,You've gotten fatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.02,0:17:53.43,Base,,0,0,0,,U-Um, I {\i1}have {\i0}gained a little weight\Nsince starting school...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.49,0:17:56.57,Base,,0,0,0,,A little? Try a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.57,0:17:58.27,Base,,0,0,0,,But, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.41,0:18:03.10,Base,,0,0,0,,Girls are cuter if they've got\Na couple of curves! Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.29,0:18:05.90,Base,,0,0,0,,What? That's just what {\i1}men {\i0}want!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.00,0:18:13.38,Base,,0,0,0,,Listen, your biggest audience is women.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.38,0:18:15.66,Base,,0,0,0,,And women have a shrewd eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.34,0:18:19.62,Base,,0,0,0,,Kouka fans want a dreamlike fantasy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.01,0:18:22.20,Base,,0,0,0,,A beauty they could never hope to obtain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.22,0:18:26.67,Base,,0,0,0,,So {\i1}no fatties{\i0}. If you want to stay here,\Nyou're going to have to shed those pounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.48,0:18:33.55,Base,,0,0,0,,I think it's a matter of self-control.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.73,0:18:36.51,Base,,0,0,0,,You're too easy on yourself, Yamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.36,0:18:40.37,Base,,0,0,0,,Stop it! She's already crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.37,0:18:43.02,Base,,0,0,0,,Be nice to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.20,0:18:46.58,Base,,0,0,0,,I'll never eat food again, I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.58,0:18:49.36,Base,,0,0,0,,No! That's not good for your health!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.75,0:18:53.96,Base,,0,0,0,,Let's ask our dorm mom for advice\Nwhen we get back, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.26,0:18:57.88,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why is she like that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.88,0:19:01.23,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why does she keep shoving herself\Ninto other people's business?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.01,0:19:04.51,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It makes her even more annoying.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.98,0:19:07.83,Base,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.11,0:19:16.99,Base,,0,0,0,,Do you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.53,0:19:20.20,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Kouka School of\NMusical and Theatrical Arts"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.74,0:19:20.20,Base,,0,0,0,,Watanabe,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.20,0:19:21.57,Base,,0,0,0,,have you seen Ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.57,0:19:23.95,Base,,0,0,0,,I think she already went back to the dorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.95,0:19:25.23,Base,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.74,0:19:30.00,Base,,0,0,0,,Y'know, Watanabe, I really hope\Nyou can be friends with Ai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.00,0:19:34.86,Base,,0,0,0,,Sure, but she told me we weren't friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.17,0:19:41.47,Base,,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to be friends with her\Nafter she said that to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.43,0:19:47.85,Base,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.85,0:19:51.13,Base,,0,0,0,,He's here. On the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.39,0:19:52.34,Base,,0,0,0,,Who's here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:55.88,Base,,0,0,0,,The guy I called a creep at that fan event.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.15,0:19:59.74,Base,,0,0,0,,Oh, God! He followed me here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.74,0:20:01.70,Base,,0,0,0,,What do I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.70,0:20:02.99,Base,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.82,0:20:06.89,Base,,0,0,0,,I'll walk you back if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.12,0:20:07.89,Base,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.08,0:20:11.16,Base,,0,0,0,,I mean, we're going back to the same room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.16,0:20:14.40,Base,,0,0,0,,I might not be your friend,\Nbut I can at least walk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.67,0:20:16.71,Base,,0,0,0,,Sure, could you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.71,0:20:17.28,Base,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.47,0:20:18.55,Base,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.55,0:20:20.55,Base,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Ai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.04,0:20:27.04,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"NOTICE: Due to increased traffic,\Nloitering and/or asking Kouka students for\Nautographs in this area is prohibited."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.01,0:20:27.56,Base,,0,0,0,,I hear that singing a fun song can help
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.56,0:20:30.60,Base,,0,0,0,,when you're feeling scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.60,0:20:33.56,Base,,0,0,0,,I'll sing something for you, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.56,0:20:41.82,Base,,0,0,0,,♬ Falling from the sky\Nlike white snow... ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.24,0:20:49.79,Base,,0,0,0,,Let go, creep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.63,0:21:01.16,Base,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! What do you think you're doing,\Nstalking a helpless girl like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.80,0:21:08.26,Base,,0,0,0,,I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.26,0:21:12.23,Base,,0,0,0,,I just, uh, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.23,0:21:15.63,Base,,0,0,0,,...just wanted to talk\Nwith Naracchi... er, Miss Narata.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.65,0:21:21.30,Base,,0,0,0,,First, here. You dropped\Nthis earlier, Naracchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.78,0:21:23.64,Base,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.00,0:21:34.84,Base,,0,0,0,,Go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.75,0:21:39.99,Base,,0,0,0,,Don't come closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.00,0:21:43.38,Base,,0,0,0,,Do you hate me 'cause I was mean to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.38,0:21:44.91,Base,,0,0,0,,Are you here to get back at me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.01,0:21:47.05,Base,,0,0,0,,I just... I--!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.18,0:21:51.60,Base,,0,0,0,,Ai!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.90,0:22:26.20,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}I'll keep walking on the path
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.20,0:22:29.86,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}that glows white in the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.86,0:22:33.38,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}A long, narrow path
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.38,0:22:35.86,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}that can only be walked alone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.86,0:22:37.61,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}I walk forward so that
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.61,0:22:42.89,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}I won't fall behind other people's shadows
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.89,0:22:46.49,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}If I just head straight forward,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.49,0:22:49.69,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}it'll appear right in front of me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.69,0:22:53.18,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}Now, let's open the door
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.69,0:22:57.90,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}There are sparkling stars in this vast sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.90,0:23:00.44,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}If just I had wings,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.31,0:23:03.01,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}I'd flap and flutter
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.01,0:23:07.02,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}high through the space like a bird
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.83,0:23:11.00,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}Going around the constellations,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.00,0:23:13.70,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}and pursuing the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.38,0:23:20.17,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}we had just started this endless journey
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.16,0:21:53.16,Base,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.04,0:23:39.96,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Act 4: Tears Overwritten"
